			R’s answer is given in circumstances specified for the purposes of thisparagraph by order of a Minister of the Crown;
			R’s failure to answer occurs in circumstances specified for the purposes ofthis paragraph by order of a Minister of the Crown.
		The reference to a contravention of this Act includes a reference to abreach of an equality clause or rule.
